  "text": "Once again, to put my claims in context I need to devote a little time to an exposition of the theory. I will concentrate on a canonical model, due to [CITATION_1] which considers the case for subsidising a single domestic firm which exports all its output (so domestic consumption can be ignored) in competition with a single foreign rival.",
